'''路易斯·厄尼斯托·阿帕里西歐·蒙提爾'''（{{lang-es|Luis Ernesto Aparicio Montiel}}，{{bd|1934年|4月29日|}}），綽號「小路易」，為美國職棒大聯盟的委內瑞拉籍游擊手。阿帕里西歐是大聯盟史上第一位入選名人堂的委內瑞拉籍選手，<ref name="Luis Aparicio at The Baseball Hall of Fame">{{cite web |url=http://baseballhall.org/hof/aparicio-luis |title=Luis Aparicio |publisher=Baseball Hall of Fame |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2011-11-02 |archive-url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20111102174455/http://baseballhall.org/hof/aparicio-luis |dead-url=no }}</ref>而他也是一名以防守和盜壘能力見長的球員。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at The Baseball Hall of Fame"/><ref name=sabrbio>{{sabrbio|87c077f1|Leonte Landino|February 4, 2012}}</ref>

1956年，阿帕里西歐拿下美聯新人王。1959年，他幫助白襪隊闖進世界大賽。1956年至1964年，他連續9年拿下美聯盜壘王寶座。另外他還拿下了9次金手套獎。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference">{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/a/aparilu01.shtml |title=Luis Aparicio |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2009-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090621075640/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/a/aparilu01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>National Baseball Hall of Fame, Luis Aparicio [http://www.baseballhall.org/hof/aparicio-luis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baseballhall.org/hof/aparicio-luis |date=20171102013611 }} Retrieved April 17, 2015</ref>而他生涯也有10個球季入選明星賽。<ref>National Baseball Hall of Fame, Luis Aparicio, "10-time All-Star" [http://www.baseballhall.org/hof/aparicio-luis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baseballhall.org/hof/aparicio-luis |date=20171102013611 }} Retrieved April 17, 2015</ref>

「打擊之神」[[泰德·威廉斯|泰德·威廉斯]]曾說過阿帕里西歐是他遇過表現最傑出的游擊手。<ref>Eldridge, Larry (January 10, 1984). "Shortstop Aparicio may be short hop from Hall of Fame, finally. The Christian Science Monitor. [http://www.csmonitor.com/1984/0110/011005.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/1984/0110/011005.html |date=20210227122815 }} Retrieved April 17, 2015</ref>1999年，阿帕里西歐還被提名至[[美國職棒大聯盟世紀球隊|美國職棒大聯盟世紀球隊]]的最終名單內。<ref name="The Major League Baseball All-Century Team">{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/mlb_history_moreinfo.jsp |title=The Major League Baseball All-Century Team |publisher=MLB.com |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2010-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100119065808/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/mlb_history_moreinfo.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==職業生涯==
===芝加哥白襪===
早在白襪隊之前，印地安人就已經打算簽下阿帕里西歐。不過當時印地安人的總經理[[漢克·格林伯格|漢克·格林伯格]]認為阿帕里西歐的身材過於嬌小，無法在大聯盟生存。<ref name=sabrbio/>反而白襪隊總經理Frank Lane聽從隊上來自委內瑞拉的好手Chico Carrasquel的建議，簽下了這位和Carrasquel同樣來自委內瑞拉的年輕小將。<ref>{{cite book |author=James, Bill |title=The New Bill James Historical Baseball Abstract |publisher=Free Press |location=New York |year=2001 |page=[https://archive.org/details/newbilljameshist00jame/page/599 599] |isbn=0-684-80697-5 |url=https://archive.org/details/newbilljameshist00jame/page/599 }}</ref>阿帕里西歐只待在小聯盟兩年就登上大聯盟，此時的他也才22歲而已。他也取代Carrasquel成為了球隊的游擊手，<ref name=sabrbio/>並在菜鳥球季成為了美聯的盜壘王。最後他拿下的美聯年度新人王，<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1956.shtml#ALroy |title=1959 Rookie of the Year Award voting results |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2009-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210021251/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1956.shtml#ALroy |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/awards/aw_snrp3.shtml |title=Rookie of the Year Award by The Sporting News |publisher=Baseball Almanac |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301014220/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/awards/aw_snrp3.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>成為第一位拿下該獎項的拉丁裔選手。<ref name=sabrbio/>

1950年代，白襪的戰績一年比一年出色。在當時，「Let's Go, Go-Go White Sox」(衝啊衝啊白襪隊)成為了當時白襪球迷的流行標語。阿帕里西歐也被認為是能夠帶領白襪重返榮耀的重要角色之一，當時他和二壘手[[內利·法克斯|內利·法克斯]]組成了完美的二游組合。<ref name="The Go-sox Go Again">{{cite web |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1132285/index.htm |title=The Go-sox Go Again |author=Terrell, Roy |publisher=Sports-Illustrated.com |date=1957-05-13 |work=Sports Illustrated |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202221748/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1132285/index.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1070879/index.htm |title=Two For The Pennant |author=Woodcock, Les |publisher=Sports-Illustrated.com |date=1959-08-10 |work=Sports Illustrated |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103011722/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1070879/index.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>1957年，這僅僅是阿帕里西歐的第二個賽季。他再度的拿下盜壘王，而且白襪隊的戰績在美聯僅次於洋基隊。<ref name="The Go-sox Go Again"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/1957-schedule-scores.shtml |title=1957 Chicago White Sox Season |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310150400/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/1957-schedule-scores.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1958年，阿帕里西歐繼續維持他不凡的身手。這年他首度入選明星賽，並成為先發游擊手。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ALS/ALS195807080.shtml |title=1958 All-Star Game |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2017-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109234532/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ALS/ALS195807080.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他一樣拿下盜壘王，白襪隊還是維持美聯第二。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/1958-schedule-scores.shtml |title=1958 Chicago White Sox Season |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308135035/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/CHW/1958-schedule-scores.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>而這年阿帕里西歐拿下了個人第一座金手套獎。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1958 |title=1958 Gold Glove Award Winners |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329233506/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1958 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1959年，白襪隊順利拿下美聯龍頭，並領先第二名的印地安人有5場勝差。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1959.shtml |title=1959 American League Final Standings |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307220159/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1959.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>Go-Go White Sox的標語也終於成真，這年隊友法克斯拿下美聯MVP，而阿帕里西歐拿下第二名。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1959.shtml#ALmvp |title=1959 American League Most Valuable Player Award voting results |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2009-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090411154731/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1959.shtml#ALmvp |dead-url=no }}</ref>在世界大賽上，阿帕里西歐的打擊率為3成08，不過最後他們不敵由[[強尼·波德瑞斯|強尼·波德瑞斯]]、[[唐·德萊斯戴爾|唐·德萊斯戴爾]]、[[山迪·柯法斯|山迪·柯法斯]]等三大強投領軍的道奇隊。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1959_WS.shtml |title=1959 World Series |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2022-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220201115458/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1959_WS.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年阿帕里西歐在前61次盜壘嘗試中成功了50次，他也毫不意外的再次拿下盜壘王。<ref>{{cite book|last=Dickson|first=Paul|title=The Dickson Baseball Dictionary|year=1989|publisher=Facts on File|location=United States|isbn=0816017417|page=[https://archive.org/details/dicksonbaseballd00dick/page/12 12]|pages=|url=https://archive.org/details/dicksonbaseballd00dick/page/12}}</ref>

1960年和1961年，阿帕里西歐仍然是美聯最好的游擊手。1962年，阿帕里西歐的體態漸漸發生變化，球隊也以減薪為由強制他減重。<ref name="If Luis Aparicio Clubhouse Lawyer, Baltimore Would Like Bench Full">{{cite news |title=If Luis Aparicio Clubhouse Lawyer, Baltimore Would Like Bench Full |agency=NEA |work=Times Daily |page=2 |date=1963-04-21 |accessdate=2011-01-04 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ehAsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=osYEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3274,5872026&dq=luis+aparicio+triandos&hl=en |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301084741/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ehAsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=osYEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3274,5872026&dq=luis+aparicio+triandos&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>阿帕里西歐對於球隊的決策感到憤怒，因此要求球隊將他交易，否則他就要退休。<ref name="If Luis Aparicio Clubhouse Lawyer, Baltimore Would Like Bench Full"/>1963年1月，白襪隊將阿帕里西歐、Al Smith交易至金鶯隊，換來Hoyt Wilhelm、Ron Hansen、Dave Nicholson和Pete Ward。<ref name="Luis Aparicio Trades and Transactions">{{cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/trades.php?p=aparilu01 |title=Luis Aparicio Trades and Transactions |publisher=Baseball Almanac |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225045929/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/trades.php?p=aparilu01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===巴爾的摩金鶯===
來到金鶯隊後，阿帕里西歐的防守率來到生涯新高的9成83。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/>他也和Jerry Adair、[[布魯克斯·羅賓森|布魯克斯·羅賓森]]組成了金鶯隊的最佳內野防守陣容。<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GS4DAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA19&lpg=PA19&dq=luis+aparicio+baseball+digest&source=bl&ots=4FXw_rXjx9&sig=AcW2BRLWOpeDuTNfFnhBXII-Htk&hl=en&ei=MYR7TOv6F4O0lQfCk9jsCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBEQ6AEwADgU#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Shortstop and Third Base Team Mates Who Led League in Fielding |author=Kuenster, John |publisher=Books.Google.com |date=June 2004 |work=Baseball Digest |accessdate=2010-08-30 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vybawTLKGmwC&pg=PA16&lpg=PA16&dq=luis+aparicio+baseball+digest&source=bl&ots=RUQm-1x0mh&sig=Ren-4ynetUT8yTAxlLFgFemaQ3c&hl=en&ei=MYR7TOv6F4O0lQfCk9jsCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CBoQ6AEwAzgU#v=onepage&q=luis%20aparicio%20baseball%20digest&f=false |title=Middle Infield Tandems That Won Fielding Titles, Same Season |author=Kuenster, John |publisher=Books.Google.com |date=June 2009 |work=Baseball Digest |accessdate=2010-08-30 }}</ref>1964年，阿帕里西歐達成盜壘王9連霸，並且拿下第6次的金手套獎。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1964 |title=1964 Gold Glove Award Winners |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329233506/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1964 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1966年，他的打擊率為3成76，並敲出182支安打。這年金鶯隊拿下了隊史首次的美聯冠軍，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1966-batting-leaders.shtml |title=1966 American League Batting Leaders |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509131847/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1966-batting-leaders.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1966 |title=1966 Gold Glove Award Winners |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329233506/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1966 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1966.shtml |title=1966 American League Final Standings |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507055224/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1966.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>並拿下了世界大賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1966_WS.shtml |title=1966 World Series |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2007-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071130235304/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1966_WS.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1966.shtml#ALmvp |title=1966 American League Most Valuable Player Award voting results |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2019-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190321234949/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1966.shtml#ALmvp |dead-url=no }}</ref>而阿帕里西歐也在MVP票選中拿下第9名。
===重回芝加哥===
不過隨著新秀Mark Belanger已經站穩了金鶯的游擊手大位，阿帕里西歐也被球隊交易。1967年11月29日，金鶯隊將阿帕里西歐、Russ Snyder和John Matias交易至白襪，換來Don Buford、Bruce Howard和Roger Nelson。<ref>[https://opensiuc.lib.siu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1017&context=de_November1967 "Trade Shuffle Sends Aparicio To White Sox," ''The Associated Press'' (AP), Thursday, November 30, 1967.] {{Wayback|url=https://opensiuc.lib.siu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1017&context=de_November1967 |date=20210303103929 }} (Scroll down to page 14.) Retrieved April 17, 2020</ref>回到白襪後，阿帕里西歐的守備能力還是一樣出色。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/>1970年，阿帕里西歐打出了生涯年。他的打擊率為生涯新高的3成13，<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/>並得到86分。他在這年入選了明星賽，並拿下第9座金手套獎。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1970 |title=1970 Gold Glove Award Winners |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329233506/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1970 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NLS/NLS197007140.shtml |title=1970 All-Star Game |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806024247/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NLS/NLS197007140.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>儘管這年白襪隊在美聯敬陪末座，不過阿帕里西歐在MVP票選上還是拿下了第12名。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1970.shtml |title=1970 American League Final Standings |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2011-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103170305/http://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1970.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1970.shtml#ALmvp |title=1970 American League Most Valuable Player Award voting results |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2009-02-22 |archive-url=https: