===波士頓紅襪===
1970年12月1日，白襪隊將阿帕里西歐交易至紅襪，換來Luis Alvarado和Mike Andrews。<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1970/12/02/archives/bob-aspromonte-joins-new-york-bostons-andrews-alvarado-sent-to.html "Bob Aspromonte Joins New York," ''The New York Times'', Wednesday, December 2, 1970.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1970/12/02/archives/bob-aspromonte-joins-new-york-bostons-andrews-alvarado-sent-to.html |date=20210308154740 }} Retrieved March 5, 2020</ref>1971年，阿帕里西歐曾一度連續44個打數沒能敲出安打，他差一個打數就要追平1909年Bill Bergen寫下的尷尬紀錄。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1084969/index.htm |title=Even The President Worried |author=Fimrite, Ron |date=1971-06-14 |work=Sports Illustrated |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103011623/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1084969/index.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他在第45個打數敲出了滿貫砲。<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=13LPw4LCj_gC&pg=PA5&dq=luis+aparicio#v=onepage&q=luis%20aparicio&f=false |title=Tales From The Red Sox Dugout |author=Prime, Jim |author2=Nowlin, Bill |publisher=Books.Google.com |isbn=1-58261-348-6 |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902174756/https://books.google.com/books?id=13LPw4LCj_gC&pg=PA5&dq=luis+aparicio#v=onepage&q=luis%20aparicio&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他的打擊率下滑至2成32，是他個人單季第二低的紀錄。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/>

1972年，阿帕里西歐在球季的最後一場比賽發生致命的跑壘失誤。最後紅襪不僅輸球，還落後給第一名的老虎半場勝差無緣季後賽。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210020.shtml |title=October 2, 1972 Red Sox-Tigers box score |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308185247/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210020.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fenwayfanatics.com/content/2007/10/02/today-in-history-base-running-blunders-doom-boston/ |title=Today In History – Base-Running Blunders Doom Boston |website=fenwayfanatics.com |date=2007-10-02 |accessdate=2018-06-20 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227221920/http://www.fenwayfanatics.com/content/2007/10/02/today-in-history-base-running-blunders-doom-boston/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1973年，他的打擊率為2成71。7月5日，阿帕里西歐完成生涯500盜。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA197307050.shtml |title=July 5, 1973 Red Sox-Yankees box score |publisher=Baseball Reference |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308150723/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA197307050.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref> 最後他在球季結束後退休。<ref name="Luis Aparicio at Baseball Reference"/>
